 Menu
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This menu is the main menu for doing a stock-take.
 It is used to restore the status of library collections that are considered
 lost by the system, In this menu, item id (barcode number) is the main
 item reference to change the status of the items that are considered lost
 to existing (there), Do this by entering the barcode number in the field
 Item Code.
 This menu will work when the Initialize process is completed.
\end_layout

