 ongoing activities to take stock of existing bibliographic data using the
 stock-take module.
 The goal is that when we do editing of bibliographic data while doing the
 stock-take, in order to produce a change in the bibliographic data contained
 in the stock-take module , it is necessary to do resynchronization of data.
 Click the button, and that Resyncronizes bibliographic data .
